[Research is making a difference. A vaccine has been conditionally licensed. This should start to make a dent in this disease and make it a preventable disease.

The state of Utah can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2750097,41315. Beaver County in western Utah can be seen on the map at http://geology.com/county-map/utah-county-map.gif. - Mod.TG]
